.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過德國又咁早出局。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T17:24:18.000Z","msg":"不要再說了.jpg<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e1c53d6fca14514ded41a305ee4ceeb8d72916","tid":734792,"uid":92017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8edc7b727a26e940d6337ab4bf7256ee9fd7d027","tid":734792,"uid":5632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T06:42:03.000Z","msg":"你地有無試過比人偷野或老笠係俄羅斯 ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T17:27:00.000Z","msg":"試過係Moscow 地鐵比一個俄仔撩，不過我有返咁上下大舊，大聲講野應佢之後，佢走開左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我感覺班俄佬都係個款惡多，我問路個陣，好多人都係兇神惡煞，但問親佢地都會好仔細教我行<br />\n有次係Moscow火車站，有個俄仔仲好熱心帶我地去買飛，仲幫我地買埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話只係想收藏下港幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但紅場個堆景點要自己查清楚規則，好似好多都唔比孭背囊入，要放係locker room，但班守衛唔識英文，只可以靠估身體語言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，所以自己查清楚穩陣<br />\n<br />\nSt.Petersberg 就完全係遊客城市，當地人感覺上寬容好多，同埋都遇到唔少香港人"},{"pid":"a9ae8518c246db82ac7b74ff553c7c4eaf4a00b2","tid":734792,"uid":92017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T17:29:58.000Z","msg":"我覺得反而你要預博物館/主要景點個班職員都幾萌塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多時係咪都會兇左你先，或者唔撚想理你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n扒手又真係完全唔覺，不過係Moscow個陣，不論條街幾大幾闊，班俄佬硬係會撞到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我最初都以為想偷野，後尾先發覺班仆街行路只會行直線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 前面有人都照撞過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed2c08197088c57fda31f0ec1cf9e533297a5785","tid":734792,"uid":92017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T17:34:30.000Z","msg":"同埋普通餐廳/快餐台同超市班職員都係比香港反應慢/萌塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地唔會理解到點解只叫野食但唔叫套餐，但佢個套餐都要加錢先有野飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你要解釋好多次佢地先唔幫你加野飲<br />\n<br />\n係火車站等搭通宵火車去St.Petersberg個陣，個收銀夾硬加我錢要野飲，我火起好躁咁屌左幾句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 排我後面個俄佬阿叔即刻幫我叫個收銀唔好搞咁多野，唔好加我野飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw，我係火車上面研究緊點開個床板出黎個陣，有個四眼俄仔行黎用普通話話幫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，佢話佢係大學副修中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d56e2b12dfb6747bae8614443e6b27d0dd50ee36","tid":734792,"uid":5632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed2c08197088c57fda31f0ec1cf9e533297a5785","tid":734792,"uid":92017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T17:34:30.000Z","msg":"同埋普通餐廳/快餐台同超市班職員都係比香港反應慢/萌塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地唔會理解到點解只叫野食但唔叫套餐，但佢個套餐都要加錢先有野飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=